spec_data.Name: WebShell
spec_data.Description:
WebShell is a standalone web server and browser application that provide
encrypted shell access through any web browser (https://host:8022). WebShell
includes a touch keyboard for use on mobile devices with a touch screen.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 03:49:00 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: SSL server for web-based SSH access from browsers and mobile devices
